The amount of work is simple:<p>h1 {
  font-size: 5vw;
}<p>The `vw` units are relative to the page width.<p>You would rather have to press the right arrow key 50 times? I find it to be a whole lot faster to scroll quickly through content rather than forcing me to click through every single damn slide.<p>EDIT: It is interesting that the vw/vh units don&#x27;t take zoom into effect, I hadn&#x27;t thought of that. Interesting.
